snippet.title: Steelrising - Cagliostro’s Secret DLC Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/product/UP6665-PPSA05064_00-STR0000000000000

Paris has many secrets, and so does Cagliostro.

Discover a new level, the Saint-Louis Hospital new enemies and character to complete your Steelrising adventure.

Aegis, it’s time to go back.  

Caliostro's Secret DLC is available now on PS5™.

Owners of the Bastille Edition of Steelrising will have instant access to this DLC. Otherwise, it can be purchased separately. 

#ps5games #ps5
